{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "悦 第4话 小悦来教你们！",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "糟了……\\n这下完全迷路了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "今天就在这里露宿吧，\\n得在天黑之前做好准备。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "露宿吗。那可少不了柴火！\\n我去找找看。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "露宿！好久没露宿了啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "来这里之前，\\n悦都是边狩猎边旅行的吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "嗯！因为以前每天都露宿野外，\\n城里的床铺反而睡不踏实！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "尤蒂尔、悦，\\n现在我们带的东西……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶……饮用水只剩下一点了？\\n这可不太妙啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是的，而且我们还没有\\n露宿用的帐篷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "哈哈哈！\\n没关系，总会有办法的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "让小悦来教教你们\\n狩猎民族是怎么露宿野外的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "首先要做睡觉的床！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "挖个能躺进4个人的洞，\\n在里面铺上草。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "把木棍插在地面上，\\n再盖上布……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "看，帐篷做好啦♪",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哇！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "好厉害……不一会儿\\n就做好了简易帐篷……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "现在可没时间发呆哦！\\n要是不抓紧，天就要黑啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "接下来要去找水！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "啊！有了有了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "藤蔓？用来做绳子吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "不是哦，这东西里面存有水分。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "像这样切开藤蔓，\\n插进水壶口……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来是这样！\\n这样水就能积起来了啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "就是这样♪好了，\\n其它水壶也按同样的方法来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "我回来了，\\n有这么多柴火应该足够了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "兰扎卜，谢谢！\\n我们这边也准备好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哟……这临时搭建的露宿地\\n看起来很舒适啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "嗯，真的呢。\\n这样就足以坚持一晚了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "都是悦的功劳，谢谢你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "诶嘿嘿……被夸了♪　",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那我们赶快生火吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不过，你是怎么学会\\n这些大自然的智慧的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "对啊……虽说是狩猎民族，\\n但也不是独自在旅行吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "嗯。不过小悦的家人\\n在族人中是最擅长狩猎的……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "所以经常会离开村落，\\n到远处去狩猎。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "往往远到没法当天往返，\\n所以常常会露宿。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶，原来悦的家人\\n在族人中也是最厉害的啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "嗯，爸爸和妈妈\\n还活着的时候……\\n都厉害又帅气呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "还活着的时候？\\n那就是说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "嗯。就在不久前，\\n两个人都死了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "被一大群野兽袭击，\\n没能战胜它们……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "怎么会……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "悦……抱歉，我们毫不知情。\\n没想到你竟然有\\n这样的悲惨经历……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "悲惨？小悦不觉得\\n自己的经历很悲惨哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "因为我们是在狩猎嘛。\\n既然如此，被狩猎也是理所当然的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "虽然不能再见面很寂寞……\\n但这也没办法！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "虽然很寂寞，\\n但没办法……吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "嗯，爸爸和妈妈已经成为了\\n这片大地的一部分。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "所以只要小悦还活在这片大地上，\\n就不是孤单一人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "唔，怎么说呢……你真是厉害。\\n虽然强大的人各有千秋， \\n但你的强大真是与众不同……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不过如果从这种角度想问题，\\n我们擅自把你的身世当作悲剧，\\n倒是有些冒昧了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "嗯。只要大地尚在，就不是孤单一人。\\n这就是悦他们一族的思考方式，\\n也是其强大之处啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊……而且，悦，\\n今后我们也能陪你一起。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "诶嘿嘿……谢谢你，\\n尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "呼啊……\\n说了好多话之后，感觉累了！\\n小悦要去睡觉啦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好。晚安，悦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "晚安～大家也早点睡觉吧！\\n休息的重要性可仅次于吃饭哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "呼噜～呼噜♪",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦！？好快！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "迅雷不及掩耳之势，\\n说的就是这种吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "像这样睡着了的话，\\n看着就是个小孩子……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，真的像个天真无邪的孩子。\\n不过就是这样的孩子……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "却有着和我们\\n完全不同的生存方式啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110056_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "悦",
            "context": "呼噜♪",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}